{"id": 1855, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得国内脱口秀/单口喜剧类节目都有哪些问题？", "description": "让不幽默的人用力搞笑，整个就是黑色幽默吧。（题图来自：Pixabay)", "record_count": 14835, "comment_count": 40, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170815015907miAxROkqd3atUg2l.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-16T17:00:39Z", "questions": [{"id": 2811, "title": "你觉得国内脱口秀/单口喜剧类节目都有哪些问题？", "content": "你觉得国内脱口秀/单口喜剧类节目都有哪些问题？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 229466, "content": "短平快的抖包袱形式照搬国外，内容质量跟不上", "image": "img/option/option/20170815021252yAtuMN2V6kEb5eSG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229467, "content": "节目尾声划重点式升华，自带弹幕的主持人：每个人都要正视自己的缺点", "image": "img/option/option/20170815020403lU9mMeXjNV5AztCH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229469, "content": "损完人马上道歉，失去单口喜剧辛辣的特点", "image": "img/option/option/201708150206298TRtioaC2lmXgVUw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229470, "content": "禁忌太多，很多社会现状材料不能拿来铺梗", "image": "img/option/option/20170815020719jzJxuIa7nZYE6hlO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229471, "content": "喜剧演员门槛太低，不能搞笑也没输出啥价值观 ", "image": "img/option/option/201708150208418jSwfN9z5LvY0ViQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229472, "content": "网络老梗整合者，有些段子的陈旧程度可以和春晚的比了", "image": "img/option/option/20170815021044mwMUAOqbY9kCXzTF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229473, "content": "明星/嘉宾硬着头皮背段子，最后不忘给自己会开玩笑的IP点题", "image": "img/option/option/20170815021230jlUe61SK08QXr52B.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229474, "content": "形式上更像真人秀，和喜剧离得有点远", "image": "img/option/option/20170815022328aEL13igHj6CTpvt0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}